</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<h4 id='id44'>打开折叠<code>z+o</code></h4>

<h4 id='id45'>打开文件中所有折叠<code>z+O</code></h4>

<h4 id='id46'>删除一个折叠<code>z+e</code></h4>

<h4 id='id47'>删除文件中所折叠<code>z+e</code></h4>

<h4 id='_'>折叠不会被写入到文件里，如果使用<code>cat</code> <code>less</code>查看代码，代码将以无任何折叠的方式显示。</h4>

<blockquote>
<p>A folder is just a tag which tells vim to display something as a folder. So it is also possible to write a file with folders. To mark the start of a folder just use for example in a comment of a source file) and to mark the end of the folder.</p>
</blockquote>

